ggest individuals in OSNs\nself-organize to create well-connected communities, while weak ties yield\ncohesion and optimize the coverage of information spread.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 2 Mar 2012 17:56:29 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 1 Nov 2014 12:49:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-11-04"}
